Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.44,0:00:02.73,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,上回的LoveLive! Sunshine!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.03,0:00:03.79,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,Aqours!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.18,0:00:06.82,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,我们通过了LoveLive!的赛前预选
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.89,0:00:07.42,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,0
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.88,0:00:08.83,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,东京？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.52,0:00:13.48,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,为了弄清楚μ's是如何拯救学校的 来到了东京
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.63,0:00:15.43,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,我觉得 μ's的厉害之处就在于
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.85,0:00:21.83,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,在一无所有的起点 一无所有的地方奋力奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.31,0:00:25.48,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,为了实现大家的心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.48,0:00:29.53,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,于是我们将要挑战LoveLive!的区域预选
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.60,0:00:37.48,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,初次见面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.93,0:00:41.13,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,我们是浦之星女子学院的校园偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.86,0:00:42.94,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,Aqours
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.32,0:00:47.49,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,今天有一件事想告诉大家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.23,0:00:50.03,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,那就是——
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.19,0:02:26.85,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,1 2 3 4 1 2 3 4
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.38,0:02:31.63,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,{\pos(326.667,594)}{\3c&HE1AD11&\blur3\4c&HFFFFFF&\fs55\fad(800,400)\pos(928,176)} Sunshine!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.61,0:02:29.87,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,3,,刚才那里的移动要加快一些
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.99,0:02:31.85,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,3,,善子的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.10,0:02:32.85,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,是夜羽！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.91,0:02:35.35,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,心态上还要再快一点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.71,0:02:36.29,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,得令
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.45,0:02:37.71,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,我会使用空间移动的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.41,0:02:40.47,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,那么来休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.81,0:02:45.49,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,太热了呐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.53,0:02:48.13,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,今天也热死人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.23,0:02:51.45,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,务必不要忘了补充水分
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.35,0:02:53.25,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.65,0:02:54.31,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,呐！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.49,0:02:58.67,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,今天也是好天气
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.53,0:03:01.17,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,不用休息么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.41,0:03:04.11,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,在太阳底下体力消耗也很快
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.77,0:03:07.19,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,毕竟果南是shiny的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.13,0:03:15.01,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,都说多少次了 最好不要穿黑色的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.53,0:03:17.71,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,黑色乃堕天使之自我所在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.71,0:03:20.63,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,若无黑色就不能茍活……
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.63,0:03:22.15,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,看你已经快死了啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.07,0:03:24.15,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,千歌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.49,0:03:27.25,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,接的好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.89,0:03:28.59,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,喝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.21,0:03:29.89,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.55,0:03:36.11,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,我很喜欢夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.89,0:03:38.31,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,感觉能燃起斗志
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.75,0:03:40.57,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.57,0:03:42.33,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.81,0:03:44.37,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,差不多继续吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.99,0:03:46.75,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.37,0:03:49.63,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,过度劳动可是大忌
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.92,0:03:51.55,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,by果南
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.55,0:03:53.55,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,她一直在为大家考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.55,0:03:54.17,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,对哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.61,0:03:56.85,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,毕竟接下来就是最热的时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.35,0:04:01.09,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,我知道LoveLive!地区预选迫在眉睫会使人焦躁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.53,0:04:04.13,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,休息也是训练的一环哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.33,0:04:05.73,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,不愧是姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.41,0:04:07.73,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,不过在那之前
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.73,0:04:09.33,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,大家拿出100日元
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.71,0:04:11.29,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,终于要来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.91,0:04:13.67,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,今日的终极诸神之黄昏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.25,0:04:17.59,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,未来啊 时间啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.01,0:04:19.73,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,我已看透！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.20,0:04:21.21,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,那就来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.72,0:04:23.24,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,剪刀石头——
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.35,0:04:27.31,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,为什么输的总是我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.47,0:04:29.37,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,一共1158日元
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.65,0:04:31.57,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,是谁要的雪糕贵了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.15,0:04:36.13,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,-zura~ -piki~ -yoha~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.53,0:04:38.53,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,风根本吹不过来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.13,0:04:42.11,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,教室里要是也有空调就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.13,0:04:44.29,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,这学校都提出要被合并了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.31,0:04:45.79,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,肯定装不了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.79,0:04:47.31,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.31,0:04:51.31,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,对了 学校说明会的参加者状况如何了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.53,0:04:54.75,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,鞠莉同学 太不像样子了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.75,0:04:56.75,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,此时此刻
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.75,0:04:58.41,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,此时此刻？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.95,0:05:00.73,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,此时此刻——
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.73,0:05:02.51,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,此时此刻——？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.01,0:05:05.59,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,0～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.69,0:05:10.31,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,这个学校就那么没有魅力么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.21,0:05:13.63,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,稍微来几个也好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.79,0:05:19.97,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,小睦你们怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.33,0:05:22.99,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,去图书室还书
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.27,0:05:25.03,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,莫非今天也要练习？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.45,0:05:27.03,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,毕竟马上就是地区预选了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.57,0:05:28.89,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,天都这么热了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.19,0:05:30.11,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,虽说如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.69,0:05:32.27,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,因为每天都这样于是就习惯了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.13,0:05:34.27,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,每天？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.27,0:05:35.51,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.03,0:05:37.51,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,每天都在练习么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.25,0:05:40.55,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,差不多要开始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.83,0:05:43.51,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,那再见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.73,0:05:46.01,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,要加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.01,0:05:50.39,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,每天都在练习啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.55,0:05:54.25,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,千歌她们在为了学校的存亡在努力着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.11,0:05:58.15,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,不过她们现在十分闪亮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.57,0:05:59.47,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,好耀眼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.67,0:06:07.87,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,今天也竭尽全力啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.87,0:06:10.65,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,不过 感觉一天比一天好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.17,0:06:13.45,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,然后 歌如何了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.45,0:06:15.73,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,刚跟花丸弄好歌词
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.73,0:06:17.73,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,现在正要跟果南确定舞蹈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.41,0:06:21.95,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,要是能让听者的heart变得shiny就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.67,0:06:25.89,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,总之为了明天 我们现在不能搞得太累
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.49,0:06:30.71,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,你又来 这样子很不成体统的！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.27,0:06:28.84,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,{\an1\pos(94,705)}嘿 堕天！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.27,0:06:30.71,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,{\an3\pos(1162,705)}Shiny
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.09,0:06:32.71,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,可是很舒服啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.32,0:06:40.90,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,啊 在这 在这
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.04,0:06:42.44,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,千歌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.67,0:06:44.31,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,小睦？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.46,0:06:46.42,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,你没有回去么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.42,0:06:47.00,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.38,0:06:50.72,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,不过 总感觉有点在意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.70,0:06:56.24,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,千歌你们在暑假里也要为了LoveLive!而练习吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.48,0:06:59.84,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,想着这样的校园偶像也挺有意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.86,0:07:05.28,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,我们也可不可以一起来当校园偶像呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.52,0:07:06.74,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,为了 拯救学校
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.30,0:07:12.34,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,其实其他人也在想着自己能不能做点什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.50,0:07:13.82,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,还挺多人的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.12,0:07:15.46,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,是这样么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.82,0:07:18.54,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,是的 之前不是说要合并废校么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.10,0:07:22.96,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,虽然大家刚开始都是觉得这无可奈何
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.42,0:07:26.56,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,不过 大家都是很喜欢这个学校的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.20,0:07:32.02,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,所以 想着拯救学校 想要绽放光芒的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.46,0:07:33.78,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,不仅仅是千歌你们
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.48,0:07:38.44,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,我们应该也可以做一些什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.22,0:07:41.84,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,千歌？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.18,0:07:43.98,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.54,0:07:48.32,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.76,0:07:49.80,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,大家一起来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.08,0:07:50.82,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,真的么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.02,0:07:51.50,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.68,0:07:52.74,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.16,0:07:54.90,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,总觉得有点兴奋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.28,0:07:57.52,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,很期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.86,0:07:58.70,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,LoveLive!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.90,0:08:00.48,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,唱歌？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.06,0:08:01.48,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.94,0:08:03.42,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,虽然跳舞不太不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.58,0:08:07.14,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,但是能一起在舞台上唱歌的话 应该来得及吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.82,0:08:08.50,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,可以么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.46,0:08:12.98,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,大家一起唱 好好地唱
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.34,0:08:16.62,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,然后变得出名了 能收到很多升学志愿书的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.88,0:08:18.64,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,学校也可以继续办下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.94,0:08:20.46,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,但是 千歌...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.46,0:08:21.00,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.72,0:08:24.40,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,现在我想要把「0」变成「1」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.06,0:08:27.54,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,今天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.22,0:08:30.26,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,跟小睦她们聊天的时候我想到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.02,0:08:33.66,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,为什么升学志愿书会是「0」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.18,0:08:38.26,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,因为 来这里的人们都很喜欢这里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.30,0:08:42.70,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,不管是小镇 学校还是人们 都很喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.30,0:08:46.58,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,也就是说 这里是一个很棒的地方对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.56,0:08:49.11,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,可如果还是「0」的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.11,0:08:51.86,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,, 就说明我们还没有把这些传达给他们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.68,0:08:56.20,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,虽然不是说「LoveLive!什么的随它去了」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.78,0:08:59.28,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,我想把「这里是一个很棒的地方」好好地传达出去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.62,0:09:00.46,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.66,0:09:03.10,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,想要把「0」变成「1」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.44,0:09:10.16,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,千...千歌...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.94,0:09:12.16,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,后...后面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.68,0:09:16.36,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,妖...妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.80,0:09:18.16,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,哇！妈妈！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.58,0:09:19.74,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,妈妈？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.06,0:09:21.28,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,那个人么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.74,0:09:25.02,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,没错 我就是高海千歌的母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.20,0:09:26.50,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,你就是梨子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.84,0:09:30.30,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,诶？是的 初次见面 晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.58,0:09:34.00,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,初次见面 晚上好 真是个美人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.22,0:09:36.82,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,倒也没有那么美啦...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.82,0:09:38.06,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,有么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.28,0:09:41.46,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,话说回来 为什么会在这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.46,0:09:43.08,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,不应该是在东京么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.60,0:09:44.58,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,虽然是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.78,0:09:51.59,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,但是志满说「千歌在当校园偶像 偶尔也回来看一次吧」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.92,0:09:53.78,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,又在做多余的事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.22,0:09:57.30,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,总之 现在我在跟梨子商量很重要的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.42,0:09:58.44,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,你先去一边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.60,0:10:01.72,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,好好 我知道了 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.44,0:10:04.00,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,可以问一个问题么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.00,0:10:04.92,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.66,0:10:07.98,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,这一次 不会放弃了么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.00,0:10:12.04,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,嗯 不会放弃的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.32,0:10:20.54,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,真是个好妈妈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.67,0:10:22.96,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,是这样么...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.70,0:10:26.44,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,总之 向着LoveLive!努力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.06,0:10:27.62,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.17,0:10:31.12,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,LoveLive! Sunshine!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.72,0:10:38.30,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,哎呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.57,0:10:39.57,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,东京？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.57,0:10:42.42,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,该来的还是会来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.55,0:10:44.96,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,汇合的地点是在...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.08,0:10:47.87,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,刚才是从这里来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.09,0:10:52.15,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,小睦她们还没来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.25,0:10:54.93,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,应该是这里没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.50,0:10:56.82,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,千歌!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.02,0:10:58.20,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,啊 来了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.39,0:10:59.65,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,在这里!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.47,0:11:03.40,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,抱歉抱歉 有点迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.07,0:11:04.94,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,其他人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.57,0:11:08.09,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,关于这个...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.57,0:11:09.71,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,其实...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.35,0:11:11.34,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.48,0:11:13.93,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,也没办法 毕竟现在是暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.43,0:11:16.60,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,我们都说过好几遍了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.38,0:11:19.51,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,但是 她们怎么样都...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.12,0:11:23.45,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,大家准备好了么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.12,0:11:29.72,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,要大家一起参加
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.84,0:11:31.79,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.15,0:11:33.31,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,吓到了么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.62,0:11:38.35,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,嗯 这样大家一起上台演唱的话绝对会非常耀眼的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.48,0:11:40.58,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,也能够传达出学校的魅力的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.77,0:11:41.60,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.16,0:11:44.95,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,梨子?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.28,0:11:50.79,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,其实我去查了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.94,0:11:54.60,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,规定能够上台演唱的只有事前入选的成员
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.04,0:11:56.17,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.72,0:12:00.17,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,而且 太接近舞台似乎也是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.84,0:12:02.98,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,要是我早点说的话就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.15,0:12:04.47,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,抱歉 小睦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.61,0:12:08.31,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,没关系 没关系 突然提出来的我们也有不对
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.62,0:12:12.80,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,那我们就在观众席上让你们看看全宇宙最强的应援
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.80,0:12:14.99,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,让大家见识浦女之魂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.15,0:12:18.09,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,所以 要让我们听听全宇宙最棒的歌曲哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.17,0:12:25.71,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,其实我还觉得难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.21,0:12:28.20,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,咱也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.87,0:12:31.86,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,现在能像这样在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.02,0:12:33.52,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,就像做梦一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.74,0:12:35.39,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,事到如今还在说些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.60,0:12:38.32,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,现在正是真实 真实正是正义
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.60,0:12:40.50,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.46,0:12:46.26,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,好了 接下来就只要成为校园偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.34,0:12:48.07,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,在舞台上堕天就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.37,0:12:51.11,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,咱是黄昏的理解者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.11,0:12:54.60,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,要上了 堕天使夜羽和小恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.92,0:12:57.97,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,降临至LoveLive!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.87,0:13:03.65,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,真没想到升上高三后会有这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.94,0:13:05.27,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,真的是没想到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.50,0:13:08.10,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,都是多亏了某人的固执
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.38,0:13:09.21,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.52,0:13:10.58,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,我很感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.40,0:13:12.13,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,鞠莉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.00,0:13:15.27,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,要道谢的是我才对
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.81,0:13:19.10,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,因为有果南和黛雅在 我才会成为校园偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.76,0:13:23.91,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,都是因为你们两个一直等着我 才能坚持到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.63,0:13:31.48,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,把当时追逐的东西 再次夺回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.25,0:13:33.63,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.21,0:13:36.35,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,真是不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.83,0:13:41.82,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,搬来内浦的时候根本没想到会有这样的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.63,0:13:44.30,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,都是因为有千歌在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.43,0:13:45.97,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,不仅仅是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.19,0:13:49.14,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,都是因为有LoveLive! 有μ's在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.24,0:13:51.05,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,有校园偶像在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.22,0:13:53.06,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,有曜和梨子在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.17,0:13:57.73,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,我想今后还会发生很多事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.43,0:14:00.22,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,不会只有开心的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.22,0:14:03.70,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,也会有很多难过的事情 辛苦的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.24,0:14:06.95,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,但我还是想期待一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.35,0:14:12.84,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,享受一切 和大家一同迈进
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.01,0:14:17.27,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,我想那一定就是所谓的 绽放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.95,0:14:19.75,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.05,0:14:22.40,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,而且我们有9人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.72,0:14:27.63,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,不只9人... 要上了!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.69,0:14:37.75,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,今天想告诉大家一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.85,0:14:43.42,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,是关于我们的学校 我们的小镇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.41,0:14:52.16,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,Aqours是从具有广阔的大海、耀眼的太阳 名为内浦的小镇中诞生的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.96,0:14:55.11,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,虽然很小也都没有人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.00,0:14:58.36,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,在海中有很多的鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.59,0:15:00.79,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,能采收到很多的蜜柑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.74,0:15:03.93,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,是充满着温暖的居民的小镇
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.26,0:15:08.52,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,在那小镇里有间很小很小的学校
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.36,0:15:10.55,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,现在在此的是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.50,0:15:12.66,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,全校的学生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.10,0:15:18.19,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,在那里 我们做起了校园偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.36,0:15:22.80,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,想变得像秋叶原看到的μ's一样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.61,0:15:25.29,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,像和她们一样闪耀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.52,0:15:27.38,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,可是……
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.02,0:15:29.04,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,作曲！？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.52,0:15:33.73,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,对 若是不会作曲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.53,0:15:37.21,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,是无法参加LoveLive!的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.53,0:15:38.69,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,难度好高！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.41,0:15:44.34,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,就在这时 懂得作曲的少女梨子转学过来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.75,0:15:45.82,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,真是奇迹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.46,0:15:48.23,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.27,0:15:56.51,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,从东京转学过来的梨子 起初对校园偶像并不感兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.47,0:15:59.43,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,因为在东京有着苦涩的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.69,0:16:01.32,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,不过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.21,0:16:03.32,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,想要绽放光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.52,0:16:07.33,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,梨子的内心里 也存在这种心愿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.72,0:16:08.43,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,接着…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.39,0:16:13.22,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,咱…我 运动不好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.72,0:16:20.14,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,露比虽然喜欢校园偶像 但是却怕生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.70,0:16:24.78,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,堕天使夜羽 在此降临
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.10,0:16:29.23,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,究竟何处才能让我舒展翅膀？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.65,0:16:34.90,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,就这样我们变为6人 放声歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.32,0:16:37.89,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,与镇上的人们一起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.96,0:16:42.83,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,这时 我们去到东京参加活动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.00,0:16:44.42,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,未来呐！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.21,0:16:45.33,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,{\pos(476,705)}好多人！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.33,0:16:47.40,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,此地即为魔都东京
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.15,0:16:49.38,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,就是要在这里唱歌吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.33,0:16:51.13,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,加油！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.29,0:16:53.03,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,然而
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.89,0:16:54.43,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,结果是……
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.33,0:16:56.94,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,最后一名
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.45,0:17:00.65,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,支持我们的人数
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.78,0:17:02.16,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,是「0」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.22,0:17:03.85,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,0
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.54,0:17:04.98,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,0
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.60,0:17:06.01,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,0
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.01,0:17:08.01,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,0
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.57,0:17:09.40,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,0
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.49,0:17:14.20,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,校园偶像的世界很残酷
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.72,0:17:17.14,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,并没有那么简单
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.90,0:17:20.37,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,要放弃么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.91,0:17:24.99,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,千歌 要放弃么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.46,0:17:28.23,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.93,0:17:30.13,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,我不甘心啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.22,0:17:34.04,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,我果然还是不甘心啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.98,0:17:37.46,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,那可是「0」啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.97,0:17:39.07,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,多不甘心啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.57,0:17:42.56,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,这时 我们找到了目标
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.79,0:17:44.83,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,从「0」迈向「1」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.67,0:17:47.60,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,不想以0结束一切
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.98,0:17:49.51,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,总之先向前进
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.94,0:17:52.55,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,把眼前的「0」变成「1」吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.98,0:17:55.01,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,没错 在内心下定决心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.18,0:17:58.11,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,就在这时 新的伙伴出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.25,0:18:01.72,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,我是学生会长黑泽黛雅
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.01,0:18:03.87,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,听说你们要做校园偶像？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.68,0:18:06.37,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,Hello, everybody
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.93,0:18:09.27,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,过去曾是校园偶像的3人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.56,0:18:11.04,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,再次牵起双手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.44,0:18:13.82,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,我们变成了9人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.89,0:18:18.13,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,就这样 我们去了LoveLive!的预选
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.54,0:18:19.81,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,结果是成功突破！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.36,0:18:23.00,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,但是 入学志愿者为0
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.81,0:18:24.94,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,不祥的0
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.08,0:18:28.62,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,再次站到了我们眼前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.87,0:18:31.44,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,为什么会是0啊——！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.32,0:18:35.31,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,我们思考着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.62,0:18:37.77,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,如何才能前进
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.24,0:18:40.58,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,如何才能将「0」变为「1」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.61,0:18:44.30,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,然后 我们决定了——
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.47,0:18:46.34,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,我们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.96,0:18:47.97,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,要与这座小镇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.45,0:18:49.63,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,要与这所学校
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.13,0:18:52.00,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,要与这些伙伴们一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.32,0:18:54.60,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,走上我们自己的路
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.20,0:18:57.46,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,接受一切现实发生的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.84,0:18:59.44,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,享受一切
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.81,0:19:03.17,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,因为 这就是「绽放光芒」！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.84,0:19:07.15,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,所谓绽放光芒 就是享受其中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.23,0:19:11.69,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,为了将那天曾是「0」的我们变成「1」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.25,0:19:16.43,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,好了 上吧
