Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.37,0:19:35.58,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,现在 尽全力绽放光芒吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.17,0:19:37.57,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,从「0」迈向「1」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.10,0:19:38.97,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,Aqours！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.35,0:19:43.01,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,Sunshine!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.25,0:21:32.40,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H0081F8&}大家！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.97,0:21:36.16,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H0081F8&}一起闪耀吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.38,0:22:56.89,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,我们从「0」制造出来的东西是什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.72,0:22:59.65,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,追逐著无形的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.15,0:23:00.90,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,彷徨著
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.44,0:23:02.19,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,害怕著
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.71,0:23:03.28,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,哭泣著
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.17,0:23:06.30,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,想从这样的「0」里面逃离出来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.29,0:23:09.94,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,但是 明明什么都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.04,0:23:12.18,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,心中却总是点着一道光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.94,0:23:16.88,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,那是相信着一定有什么事是只有我们9个人才能做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.16,0:23:18.96,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,信任之光
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.86,0:23:23.26,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,我们Aqours就是从这里诞生的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.33,0:23:25.69,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,会实现给你们看的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.24,0:23:27.98,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,我们的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.84,0:23:30.17,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,凭借这份光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.66,0:23:32.97,AQ-ANIME,,0,0,0,,你的内心
